data.description: Welcome to this cozy A-Frame that has been beautifully updated! Downstairs offers a living room, kitchen and full bathroom that was remodeled with large tile flooring, new tub with handheld spout. The living room has insulated vinyl floors installed in 2019, tongue and groove ceiling with two-stage lights, and pellet stove with a slate landing. Upstairs has vaulted ceilings and space for an office or additional bedroom with a balcony. The spacious primary bedroom has a full bathroom with extra sink in bedroom, walk-in closet, and access to the backyard and epoxy-sealed garage. The spacious lot is lined with trees giving it a private feeling, along with a chicken coop and storage shed in the backyard. The Little Deschutes River is across the street as well as access to trails and all La Pine has to offer!
